data.value: Have you considered donating yet?!? A lot of hard work and graft went into this release. It's really simple to donate; just click the button below or visit http://script-o-matic.net and click the Donate button there. There's also a donation button located on the main form! We hope you enjoy this release; however be nice (security team are actually good people in Finland) :-)
